+- Confirm current Sessions tab behavior and routes.
+- Identify shared UI pieces that Projects can copy without refactoring the whole app.
+- Define final V1 TypeScript contracts for:
+  - `PiboProject`,
+  - `WorkflowDefinition`,
+  - `WorkflowRun`,
+  - `WorkflowNodeDefinition`,
+  - `WorkflowEdgeDefinition`,
+  - `WorkflowTraceEvent`,
+  - `WorkflowSessionLink`.
+- Decide whether the first Project store wraps `PiboRoomStore` or creates a dedicated table.
+- Decide the first debug CLI command names for workflow inspection.
+
+Deliverables:
