+- Project API facade,
+- workflow read endpoints,
+- Projects sidebar data,
+- Workflow status panel.
+
+This PR makes the feature visible.
+
+### PR 5: Standard Project Skeleton And Feedback Actions
+
+Purpose: ship the first useful product workflow.
+
+Scope:
+
+- `standard-project` registration,
+- skeleton flow,
+- feedback actions,
+- traceable complete/fail/discard states.
+
+### PR 6: Runtime Node Adapter
+
+Purpose: connect Workflow nodes to real Pibo Sessions and runtimes.
+
+Scope:
+
+- runtime node adapter,
+- Session link bridge,
+- runtime trace correlation,
+- worker/worktree metadata where available.
+
+## 10. Testing Strategy
+
+### Unit Tests
+
+- Workflow definition validation.
+- Workflow store persistence.
+- Trace event ordering.
+- Runner transitions and retries.
+- Project API serialization.
+
+### Integration Tests
+
+- Start Workflow Run.
+- Resume waiting run.
+- Discard run.
+- Link Workflow Run to Pibo Session.
+- Fetch Workflow Run and trace through Chat Web API.
+
+### Browser Checks
+
+- Sessions tab still works.
+- Projects tab opens.
+- Project list/select works.
+- Workflow status appears.
+- User feedback buttons work.
+
+### Manual Debug Checks
+
+```text
+npm run dev -- debug workflow list
+npm run dev -- debug workflow show <workflowRunId>
+npm run dev -- debug workflow trace <workflowRunId>
+```
+
+## 11. Rollback Strategy
+
+The feature should be additive.
+
+If Projects breaks:
+
+- hide or disable Projects tab,
+- leave Sessions tab intact,
+- keep Workflow store data for debugging,
+- do not migrate or delete Room data during the MVP.
+
+If Workflow execution breaks:
+
+- keep Projects tab in read-only or empty-state mode,
+- disable starting new Workflow Runs,
+- keep existing Sessions workflows available.
+
+## 12. Open Implementation Questions
+
+- Should Project storage wrap `PiboRoomStore` for the first PR or use a new `pibo_projects` table immediately?
+- Should Projects show Sessions grouped by Workflow Run or Workflow Runs grouped by Project first?
+- What exact route should represent a Workflow Run: `/projects/:projectId/workflows/:workflowRunId` or `/projects/:projectId/sessions/:piboSessionId` with workflow context?
+- Which debug CLI namespace should own Workflow commands?
+- Which Standard Project nodes should remain function nodes until runtime adapter work lands?
+- How much Session UI should be extracted before copying, and how much duplication is acceptable for the first Projects tab?
+- Which cleanup actions belong in V1 versus a later System Update workflow slice?
