+---
+title: Pibo Workflow MVP Architecture
+version: 0.1
+date_created: 2026-05-07
+last_updated: 2026-05-07
+owner: Pibo
+status: draft
+tags: [architecture, workflows, mvp, state-machine, graph, runtime, sessions, tracing, persistence]
